@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kkfocf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.98
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.53) - (v2 + 0.21 / tmp + 0.71)) * ((v1 + 0.74 - v1 + 0.94) / v1))
    v0 = wp.sin((v2 * (v2 + 0.08 - v0 + 0.32)))
    v0 = (v2 - ((v2 + 0.24 * v0 + 0.63) / 0.06))
    data[tid] = v0
